# UI Components

## Component Structure
- Reusable UI components are in [src/components/ui](mdc:src/components/ui)
- These are based on Shadcn/UI components configured in [components.json](mdc:components.json)
- Custom app-specific components are in [src/components](mdc:src/components)

## Styling
- Uses Tailwind CSS with config in [tailwind.config.mjs](mdc:tailwind.config.mjs)
- Global styles are in [src/app/(frontend)/globals.css](mdc:src/app/(frontend)/globals.css)
- CSS variables are defined in [src/cssVariables.js](mdc:src/cssVariables.js)

## Key Component Categories
- Navigation: [app-sidebar.tsx](mdc:src/components/app-sidebar.tsx), [nav-*.tsx](mdc:src/components/nav-main.tsx)
- User-related: [UserProfile](mdc:src/components/UserProfile), [UserSkill](mdc:src/components/UserSkill)
- Dialogs and forms: Various Dialog* components throughout the app
- Data display: Tables, charts, and skill matrices
